<%= page_title "Product recall tool" %>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-three-quarters">
    <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">
      Preparing product recall information
    </h1>
    <p class="govuk-body-l opss-secondary-text">
      Preparing and formatting <abbr title="Product Safety Database">PSD</abbr> data for the Product Recalls and Alerts digital service.
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body-s opss-secondary-text">
      –&nbsp;<a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/product-recalls-and-alerts" class="govuk-link govuk-link--no-visited-state" target="_blank">Product Recalls and Alerts (opens in a new tab)</a>
    </p>
    <hr class="govuk-section-break govuk-section-break--xl govuk-section-break--visible">
  </div>
</div>
<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-three-quarters">
    <p class="govuk-body">
      This tool provides a convenient process for porting information from the <abbr>PSD</abbr> to the Product Recalls and Alerts digital service. It will generate a <abbr title="Portable Document Format">PDF</abbr> (with product images) and you can add or edit information before transforming it into the required Markdown format, ready to ‘copy and paste’ directly into the recall service.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    <%= @product.product_name_with_cases %>
    <div class="govuk-form-group">
      <a href="<%= product_recall_path(product_id: @product.id, id: "select-images") %>" role="button" draggable="false" class="govuk-button govuk-button--start">
        Start now
        <svg class="govuk-button__start-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17.5" height="19" viewBox="0 0 33 40" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
          <path fill="currentColor" d="M0 0h13l20 20-20 20H0l20-20z"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
